			<tr>
				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Do people in other classes actually know how bards solo?<a name="33772"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Apr 9 04 9:24 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span><blockquote><b>Quote:</b><br><span class="quote">Have you ever charm soloed PoP with a druid? I have, and I can tell you that once you get good at it, the xp is great, and IMO it's easier than swarming</span></blockquote>
<br />

<br />
Hmm... by PoP do you mean Frogs in PoS? Cause there isn't really many animals around for dr00ds to charm. And if so, have you taken into account how long it takes to go find a frog? Not to mention (if you doing PoS Frogs in Forest camp) you run out of them after 6th kill or so and have to wait/med for them to spawn?
<br />

<br />
If there were unlimited amount of frogs then it would be decent experience, but alas, that ain't the case. Still, awesome exp for a dr00d I guess<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-4.gif" border="0" alt="Tongue out" hspace="2" />
<br />

<br />
Hurricane frogs are level 60-61. Typhoon frogs are level 60.
<br />

<br />
My bard charm kites in PoN the 9 Hoggoblins (level 56) you can pull without agroing the named caster ones. Then, while waiting for them to respawn goes and pulls 10-15 Nettlin Wraiths (level 55), and when bored I even agro Big spiders (level 57-61) along with the Wraiths that proc FD on charmed pet, cracks me up everytime <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-13.gif" border="0" alt="LOL" hspace="2" />. 
<br />

<br />
In all, it would be 20+ level 55-56 mobs in 30 minutes. Kill speed &gt; All (specially since frogs and hoggoblins are only 4 levels away). 
<br />

<br />
And charm kite is so safe it almost feels like a cheat. I have only died 1 time due to LD. 
<br />

<br />
The only solo experience faster than Charm Kiting stuff in PoN with bard that I have found is Chanter Charm in HoH. My chantie will wipe Human Hall camp at HoH zone in about 25 mins (12 Valorians Guard/Sentry [level 62-63 mobs], 2 Hero Shrine Guards [level 60-61] and every once in a blue moon 2 level 66 mobs will spawn as well).
<br />

<br />
However, while relatively safe, I do die more often with chanter than with bard since running is not an option.
<br />

<br />
<blockquote><b>Quote:</b><br><span class="quote">How are these not comparable?</span></blockquote>
<br />

<br />
They are not. 
<br />

<br />
You are comparing a 63 druid (charm is level 63 - dr00d prolly 65) with your level 57 bard experiences. Get to 64, try charm kiting Hogobblins and Wraiths and then compare them.
<br />

<br />
And while at it, get Fading Memories and stop wasting money on GATE potions <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-2.gif" border="0" alt="Big Smile" hspace="2" /> </span></td>
